text.autoconfig.chesttracker.title: Chest Tracker Config
text.autoconfig.chesttracker.option.trac: Sometimes, the mod may remember items that should not be remembered (such as a crafting table, where any items in the grid are dropped when you close out, or a horse which is an entity). This screen allows you to prevent certain GUIs from being saved. To see the correct name to use, enable "§aPrint GUI names in chat§f".
